
Overview of noun accusation

The noun accusation has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (3) accusation, accusal -- (a formal charge of wrongdoing brought against a person; the act of imputing blame or guilt)
2. accusation, charge -- (an assertion that someone is guilty of a fault or offence; "the newspaper published charges that Jones was guilty of drunken driving")
